About us
Welcome  to Casey Jones RV Park
We are family owned and operated. Whether this is your first stay with us, or you have returned, we want you to feel at home here. If you are satisfied, please tell others, if not, please tell us. Your goodwill means everything to us, and we appreciate you staying with us.
Our address is 185 SW Arrowhead Terrace, Lake City, FL 32024
Columbia County  1-75 Exit 423, S.R. 47 South/Right On S.R. 242
Feel Free to  call or E-mail Me with any questions you may have at
386-755-0471
snpglenn@aol.com
Please put the word “Reservations" in the subject title, this way I will not  delete it by mistake. I will check mail everyday and answer any questions you may have.
Thank You Colin Glenn (owner)
